&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cHM6Ly93ZWJydGMuZ2l0aHViLmlvL3NhbXBsZXMvc3JjL2NvbnRlbnQvY2FwdHVyZS9jYW52YXMtcGMv&#34;&gt;从画布元素流式传输到对等连接&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cHM6Ly93ZWJydGMuZ2l0aHViLmlvL3NhbXBsZXMvc3JjL2NvbnRlbnQvY2FwdHVyZS9jYW52YXMtcmVjb3JkLw==&#34;&gt;从画布元素记录流&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cHM6Ly93ZWJydGMuZ2l0aHViLmlvL3NhbXBsZXMvc3JjL2NvbnRlbnQvY2FwdHVyZS92aWRlby1jb250ZW50aGludC8=&#34;&gt;使用内容提示指导视频编码&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
